Ing '''Globe Telecom''' ({{Pse|GLO}}), a mas kilala king lagyung '''Globe''', ing kadwang pekamaragul a cumpania king [[:en:telecommunications]] king mabilug a  [[Filipinas]].

==Kasalesayan==
Manibat pa kanitang panaun da reng Americanu ing umpisa ning Globe Telecom, ketang metung a kumpanyang maki lagyung [[Dollaradio]], a mitatag kanitang dekadang 1920.  Anya muring dekadang ita, minaliwa ya lagyu ing kumpanya, at megi yang [[Globe Wireless Limited]] (GWL).

Kanitang [[January 15]], [[1935]], mekisanib ya ing GWL kareng adwang kumpanya, ing [[Philippine Press Wireless]] (PREWI), ampo ing [[Mackay Radio Telegraph]], at linto ya ing metung a bayung kumpanya, ing [[Globe-Mackay Cable and Radio Corporation]], o GMCR.  Ketang [[1974]], pisali ne ning GMCR ing 60% ning kayang stock king [[Ayala Corporation]].

Kanitang decadang 1990, misanib ya ing Globe ampo ing aliwa pang cumpania, ing [[Clavecilla Radio System]] (CRS), at ini ing penibatan ning bayung Globe Telecom.  Anyang [[1993]], Misaup ya ing [[Ayala Corporation|Ayala]] ampo ing [[Singapore Telecommunications]] (Singtel), deng makibandi king cumpania, bang mitikdo ing kayang sikanan king telecomunicacion.  Ketang [[2001]], asali ne ning Globe ing  [[Isla Communications]], or Islacom, metung a cumpaniang halus mengalugi na, a maki kaugnayan kareng cellphone at teleponung landline. Megi yang yang Innove Communications kanitang [[2003]] itang dake nang maki kaugnayan kareng landline, lalam ning lagyung Globelines.  Samantala, miragdag naman ketang metung a cumpaniang makalalam king Globe, ing Globe Handyphone, itang serbisyu na king cellphone.     

==Cumpaniang bandi o makalalam==
Deng makatuking cumpania ing bibilug king Globe Telecom :
*[[Globe Handyphone]] (mobile carrier)
*[[Globe Solutions]] (business solutions)
*[[Innove Communications]] (fixed-line carrier and Internet service provider)
*[[Touch Mobile]] (mobile carrier)

